.py](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/tests/test_geometry_contract.py). I also aligned [pipeline_notes.md](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/docs/pipeline_notes.md) and [operator_bundle_design.md](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/docs/operator_bundle_design.md).\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n**Verified**\\\\\\\\n- Ran `make test`.\\\\\\\\n- Result: 34 tests passed, 0 failed.\\\\\\\\n- The new fixture coverage checks deterministic fine-operator output, sparse shape/sparsity consistency, symmetry and PSD expectations, zero row-sum stiffness, tangent-frame integrity, geodesic-neighborhood structure, and open-mesh boundary-mask behavior.\\\\\\\"}}\\\\n\\\",\\\"exit_code\\\":0,\\\"status\\\":\\\"completed\\\"}}\\nagent_tickets/runs/20260321T185349Z/FW-M6-006_Run_a_Milestone_6_implementation_verification_pass_and_publish_a_readiness_report/stdout.jsonl:9:{\\\"type\\\":\\\"item.completed\\\",\\\"item\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"item_2\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"command_execution\\\",\\\"command\\\":\\\"/bin/bash -lc 'git status --short'\\\",\\\"aggregated_output\\\":\\\" M Makefile\\\\n M agent_tickets/runs/20260321T185349Z/FW-M6-004_Add_configurable_boundary-condition_and_anisotropy_plumbing_to_operator_assembly/stdout.jsonl\\\\n M config/visual_subset.example.yaml\\\\n M docs/operator_bundle_design.md\\\\n M docs/pipeline_notes.md\\\\n M scripts/03_build_wave_assets.py\\\\n M src/flywire_wave/config.py\\\\n M src/flywire_wave/geometry_contract.py\\\\n M src/flywire_wave/mesh_pipeline.py\\\\n M src/flywire_wave/surface_operators.py\\\\n M tests/fixtures/operator_metadata_fixture.json\\\\n M tests/test_config_paths.py\\\\n M tests/test_geometry_contract.py\\\\n M tests/test_mesh_pipeline_build.py\\\\n M tests/test_surface_operators.py\\\\n?? agent_tickets/runs/20260321T185349Z/FW-M6-004_Add_configurable_boundary-condition_and_anisotropy_plumbing_to_operator_assembly/last